President Uhuru Kenyatta has issued a stern warning against anyone found flouting the ban on political gatherings for the next 30 days. This comes against the backdrop of numerous rallies occasioned by various by-elections and the building bridges initiative. As ODM party leader Raila Odinga who has tested positive of covid-19 continues to recuperate, Kenyans are now demanding all the politicians, who came into contact with him to self isolate